news.title: Pune: Lookout notices for Narayan Rane's wife, MLA son over Rs 65 crore unpaid loans
news.para: The LOCs have been authorised by three parties, including the Union Home Ministry, the lender, and the financial institution (Dewan Housing Finance Ltd), followed by a complaint by Maharashtra government on August 20.

news.title: Coimbatore corporation's engineers, TP officials to stop building plan violations together
news.para: The town planning section is responsible for approving building plans, regularising them and clearing encroachments. The section is short staffed to meet the workload prevailing in the city, sources said.

news.title: Property tax amnesty scheme for residents living in Lal Dora, other areas: NDMC
news.para: The NDMC has rolled out a new amnesty scheme in order to provide relief to the residents living in areas falling within Lal Dora, extended Lal Dora, extended 'abadi' of village and 544 unauthorised regularised colonies and unauthorised colonies and properties allotted to the Kashmiri migrants, officials said.
